ont-size:14px;\">{EMAIL}</span><br style=\"padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;\" />\r\n工作时间：周一至周五【09:00—17:00】\r\n							</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div style=\"border-bottom:#cccccc 1px;padding-bottom:10px;overflow-x:hidden;overflow-y:hidden;border-right-style:none;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;width:680px;padding-right:0px;border-top-style:none;border-left-style:none;padding-top:10px;border-image:initial;\" class=\"about_ad_piece piece_con\">\r\n		<div style=\"padding-bottom:0px;overflow-x:hidden;overflow-y:hidden;margin:0px;padding-left:35px;width:580px;padding-right:0px;float:left;padding-top:0px;\">\r\n			<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:28px;margin-top:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;\" class=\"bout_ad_piece_content\">\r\n				<br style=\"padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"line-height:21px;background-color:#ffffff;font-family:arial;white-space:normal;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span> \r\n			</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 18, 999999, '广告合作', '广告合作', 1343976838, 0),
